subject: Tennis
Family Circle Cup (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams defeated her older sister Venus, 6-1, 6-2, in a Family Circle Cup semifinal that lasted 54 minutes. Serena has won 14 of their 24 meetings.
